:R-HSA-8984722  a           owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_0070757 ;
        rdfs:comment        "Interleukin 35 (IL35) is an IL12 family cytokine produced by regulatory but not effector T-cells. It is a dimeric protein composed of IL-12RB2 and IL27RA chains. IL35 suppresses inflammatory responses of immune cells." ;
